# NAME: Apple China Direct
# AUTHOR: Codex
# UPDATED: 2026-06-14
# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: Apple Support, SukkaW/Surge, felixonmars/dnsmasq-china-list, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script
# NOTE: Apple services with Mainland China regional endpoints or CDN delivery.
# NOTE: Apply this ruleset to DIRECT before broader Apple or AI rules when Mainland China routing is intended.
# NOTE: Overlaps AI.list on Siri/Smoot and Speedtest.list on Apple netQuality; Surge uses the first match.

